                     <interp inst="t18440701-1842-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp> for stealing 1 shawl, value 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440701-name-280" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18440701-name-280" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
